item.title: If It Were Realistic - Quick Scope (Call of Duty Black Ops Machinima)
item.description:
If It Were Realistic - Quick Scope (Call of Duty Black Ops Machinima)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s-ntFS60_gs Click here to watch If It Were Realistic: If It Were Realistic: Jetpacks (Halo Reach Machinima) If It Were Realistic: Quick Scope (Call of Duty Black Ops Machinima) Quickscoping is total nonsense in Black Ops and in MW2. It is a divisive issue because it is both realistic and unrealistic . I mean, there are people talented enough to pick up a sniper rifle, and shoot a target from a far distance in very little time, but this is the exception and not the rule. Also, they wouldn't be doing it in somebodies face because that would be dumb. Instead of making this video comedic and poke fun at something unrealistic we decided to do a 180 and just do a cool short about how a real quickscope might work.
